{"tid":718633,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片睇】Hello Kitty 新幹線 6 月 30 日投入服務　粉紅車廂打卡必去","createTime":"2018-06-26T23:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T23:55:27.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fca2e7ffb3deb39990ba5ba7f05fc1e987bc157e","tid":718633,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:43:40.000Z","msg":"JR 西日本早前推出新世紀福音戰士新幹線後，早1已公布即將夥拍與 Sanrio 家族，推出 Hello Kitty 新幹線。昨日（25日）， JR 正式宣布將以早前的新世紀福音戰士新幹線  500 系列車改裝成Hello Kitty 新幹線，並於 6 月30 日開始投入服務，來往大阪及九洲博多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-26_173420.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-26_173420.png&h=5d478585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-06-26-17.48.35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-06-26-17.48.35.png&h=568150f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-06-26-17.51.40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-06-26-17.51.40.png&h=9ae841b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車身外裝採用 Hello Kitty 標誌性的粉紅色絲帶及蝴蝶結作裝飾，車頭及車尾亦畫有 Kitty 車長版。而內裝亦充滿 Hello Kitty 要素，車廂內亦設有途經 8 個縣的特色彩繪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/20180329171017_1_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F20180329171017_1_2.jpg&h=6472d12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從宣傳片段中可見，新幹線內部共有 2 種配置。主要座位區的椅子、扶手及窗框等都印滿 Hello Kitty ，更設有立體 Hello Kitty 拍照點，讓乘客拍照留念。此外，列車亦設有全粉紅色的陳設車廂，用作宣傳食物及觀光資訊，更可購買當地特產。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-06-26-17.49.05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-06-26-17.49.05.png&h=ae82b3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-26_174052.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-26_174052.png&h=5bd35ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-26_174031.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-26_174031.png&h=a64624a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-26_174009.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-26_174009.png&h=4c2e03d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-06-26-17.49.42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-06-26-17.49.42.png&h=f9abebe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-06-26-17.48.19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-06-26-17.48.19.png&h=2fd86d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在博多總站， JR 西日本更早於本月初，就開設了 Hello Kitty 主題咖啡廳，不論是剛到埗還是正在等車的旅客，都能夠享受到特別的 Hello Kitty 飲品及食物。 Hello Kitty 新幹線每日只有 1 班，而且一般旅客只需購買新幹線特急券及乘車券即可乘坐，想和 Hello Kitty 一起坐火車的旅客，就要先查閱班次時間，及早購買車票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-26_173830.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-26_173830.png&h=50007148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方網頁：<a href=\"http://www.jr-hellokittyshinkansen.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jr-hellokittyshinkansen.jp%2F&d=%2BJAk%2FLh3C89cP9fo2tcC3QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4532cf9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jr-hellokittyshinkansen.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/06/26/hello-kitty-shinkansen/life-tech/travel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2Fhello-kitty-shinkansen%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2F&d=%2BJAk%2FLh3C89cP9fo2tcC3QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5011ce5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/06/26/hello-kitty-shinkansen/life-tech/travel/</a>"},{"pid":"45da16b0a6888156068e3d31cf07bee2191b9937","tid":718633,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:55:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Y0F3ZOsLzUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY0F3ZOsLzUg&d=%2BJAk%2FLh3C89cP9fo2tcC3QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=aa358bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Y0F3ZOsLzUg</a>"}]}